06:18.073 --> 06:19.291
YOUR MUSCLES COULD CRAMP UP.

06:21.598 --> 06:23.426
TRUST ME, I'M A LIFEGUARD.

06:24.819 --> 06:26.255
-I SAW YOU
AT THE FIGHTS TODAY.

06:26.386 --> 06:28.213
DIDN'T SEEM LIKE
YOU LIKED IT MUCH.

06:28.779 --> 06:32.827
-YEAH, WELL, I DON'T THINK
THAT KICKBOXING IS A SPORT
OR AN ART.

06:32.957 --> 06:34.524
I THINK IT'S BARBARIC.

06:35.482 --> 06:37.309
-YEAH, I GUESS
IT CAN BE, SOMETIMES.

06:38.136 --> 06:39.486
-YEAH, BUT THEN,
WHY DO YOU DO IT?

06:39.616 --> 06:42.532
-'CAUSE IT'S ALSO MY WAY OUT.
-OF WHAT?

06:42.663 --> 06:45.709
-WHERE I'VE BEEN, WHERE I AM.
-WHERE'S THAT?

06:45.840 --> 06:47.842
-YOU KNOW, YOU ASK
A LOT OF PERSONAL QUESTIONS

06:47.972 --> 06:49.626
FOR SOMEONE WHOSE NAME
I DON'T EVEN KNOW.

06:49.757 --> 06:53.325
-OH, I'M SORRY.
MY NAME'S SUMMER,
SUMMER QUINN.

06:54.326 --> 06:58.809
-SUMMER. THAT'S A PRETTY NAME.
I'M STEVE, STEVE THORN.

07:04.162 --> 07:06.687
-WHAT'S THIS?
-IT'S CALLED A PILATE MACHINE.

07:06.817 --> 07:09.733
AS FAR AS I'M CONCERNED,
IT'S THE BEST DAMN THING
EVER INVENTED.

07:09.864 --> 07:11.256
A LITTLE STRENGTH
AND FLEXIBILITY.

07:11.387 --> 07:12.910
PUT YOUR HEAD
RIGHT THROUGH HERE.

07:13.041 --> 07:15.304
OKAY, BACK FLAT, LEGS UP.

07:15.435 --> 07:17.698
OKAY, LEG THROUGH THERE,
LEG HERE.

07:17.828 --> 07:19.830
-SO, WHAT'S GOING ON
WITH THIS GUY NAMED BRANSON?

07:19.961 --> 07:21.876
-WILL YOU FORGET
ABOUT BRANSON, HUH?

07:22.006 --> 07:24.574
LEGS STRAIGHT. OKAY, UP.
GO ALL THE WAY UP,
ON YOUR SHOULDERS.

07:24.705 --> 07:26.315
ALL THE WAY UP.
-OKAY.

07:26.446 --> 07:28.535
-COME DOWN REAL SLOW.
REAL SLOWLY.

07:29.231 --> 07:31.842
OKAY, BRING THEM DOWN
ALL THE WAY.

07:31.973 --> 07:34.932
OKAY, NOW FOLLOW UP.
UP, UP. FEEL THAT?

07:35.063 --> 07:36.934
-YES, I FEEL IT.
-FEEL THAT IN YOUR BACK? YEAH?

07:37.065 --> 07:38.675
-YES.
-PULLED TIGHT?

07:38.806 --> 07:40.111
-OH, WHAT, ARE YOU GONNA
TORTURE HIM INTO WINNING?

07:40.242 --> 07:42.200
-COME TO SPY
FOR THE OTHER SIDE?

07:42.331 --> 07:43.767
-WHAT ARE YOU GRUNTING ABOUT?

07:44.594 --> 07:45.769
-DO ME A FAVOR.
SPOT HIM, WILL YA?

07:45.900 --> 07:47.292
WHEN HE GETS UP
ON HIS SHOULDERS,

07:47.423 --> 07:48.772
MAKE SURE HE COMES DOWN
ONE VERTEBRAE AT A TIME.

07:48.903 --> 07:50.382
I'LL GET YOU SOMETHING
FOR YOUR MUSCLES.

07:56.171 --> 07:58.129
HEY, C.J., YOU OKAY?

07:59.174 --> 08:01.045
-I DON'T KNOW.

08:01.176 --> 08:02.046
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

08:03.047 --> 08:03.918
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

08:04.919 --> 08:07.443
-I MET THIS FRENCH PHOTOGRAPHER
ON THE BEACH TODAY,

08:07.574 --> 08:10.838
AND HE WANTS ME TO TRY OUT FOR
"SPORTS WORLD INTERNATIONAL,"
THE BATHING SUIT EDITION.

08:10.968 --> 08:13.057
HE SAYS I CAN MAKE
A LOT OF MONEY AS A MODEL.

08:14.276 --> 08:16.844
-A PHOTOGRAPHER ASKED ME TO POSE
FOR HIM ON THE BEACH ONCE.

08:17.671 --> 08:20.195
-REALLY?
-SAID IT WAS FOR
HIS COLLEGE THESIS.

08:20.325 --> 08:22.414
I ENDED UP ON THE COVER
OF A CALENDAR,

08:22.545 --> 08:24.547
WITH NAKED WOMEN
IN LIFE VESTS.

08:24.678 --> 08:26.201
THE COUNTY WASN'T TOO PLEASED.

08:26.331 --> 08:28.769
-ALAIN BEGERE IS LEGITIMATE.
I CHECKED HIM OUT.

08:28.899 --> 08:31.423
-[IN FRENCH ACCENT]
SO, WHAT IS THE PROBLEM?

08:31.554 --> 08:34.296
THE PROBLEM IS, I DON'T KNOW
IF I WANT MY LIFE TO CHANGE.
I KIND OF LIKE IT THE WAY IT IS.

08:35.078 --> 08:36.124
-THEN, DON'T DO IT.

08:36.254 --> 08:37.647
-BUT IT COULD BE
REALLY EXCITING,

08:37.778 --> 08:39.606
AND I COULD DEFINITELY
USE THE MONEY.

08:39.736 --> 08:41.956
-THEN, DO IT.
-BUT WHAT IF IT'S
REALLY EMBARRASSING?

08:42.086 --> 08:44.044
