SELF-CONSCIOUS AND LOOK STUPID?

08:44.174 --> 08:45.742
-THEN, DON'T DO IT.

08:46.482 --> 08:48.745
-BUT--
-C.J., I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

08:50.442 --> 08:52.227
