08:53.924 --> 08:55.012
ODDS, YOU DO IT.

08:56.753 --> 08:57.754
EVENS, YOU DON'T.

09:20.560 --> 09:21.517
ALAIN: ANGRIER.

09:22.736 --> 09:25.303
[SPEAKING FRENCH]

09:26.522 --> 09:30.265
PUT YOUR HEAD SIDEWAYS. YES.
SUSIE, DROP DOWN. YES.

09:31.832 --> 09:36.619
YES. YES. ATTITUDE.
LIKE FLOWING WINE.

09:38.621 --> 09:42.146
VOILA. OKAY. MORE HAIR.
HAIR, GINGER.

09:43.234 --> 09:45.933
MORE. YES.

09:46.063 --> 09:49.458
OKAY. HAPPY.
VOILA, GIRLS. OKAY.

09:50.981 --> 09:51.808
PEGGY.

09:52.983 --> 09:54.332
