TO ANOTHER PARKING LOT?

18:40.119 --> 18:42.469
YEAH, I LIVE IN MY CAR.
IS THAT OKAY WITH YOU?

18:43.339 --> 18:46.125
-LOOK, I BROUGHT YOU THIS.
-DID YOU MISS SOMETHING?

18:46.255 --> 18:48.562
