NOTHING TO ME!

18:51.521 --> 18:54.829
-STEVE!
-LOOK, GET OUT OF HERE
AND LEAVE ME ALONE!

19:03.881 --> 19:05.144
-CAREFUL. YOU DON'T WANT
TO HURT THAT HAND.

19:05.274 --> 19:06.928
IT'S A VALUABLE ASSET.

19:07.058 --> 19:10.192
